name: Gather Community Plant #012 - Gabriel "köi"
description:
The Gather Community Plant Collection features works from HicEtNunc artists and their artistic renditions of the GatherArt plant. The plant signifies beginnings, growth, eco friendliness, and the concept of nurturing what we love.

Gabriel "köi" is a Brazilian visual artist with a fascination for animation and generative art.

Collecting this plant directly supports GatherArt & the artist who planted this CleanNFT.
